cross: Sarcochilus Kulnura Dazzel x Sarcochilus Kulnura Vibrance

measurements.description: Two hundred fifty-four flowers and 30 buds on 26 inflorescences average 20cm long; well-grown multiple growth plant, 43cm tall by 58cm wide, 17-cm plastic pot; sepals and petals dusty rose; lip white overlaid orange, sidelobes white, fine dusty rose spots; column white, anther cap white; substance firm; texture matte.
